Text: It was my first trip to Srinagar which is called as heaven on earth.... Which
  truly was ..... As I was with my family members in this trip ... My mom dad grandma
  and big bro. It was summer we thought there the weather will me normal as in jamu
  it was deadly hot... So we decided to wear shorts and sliveless shirt .... As we
  were going near to Srinagar my god the atmosphere become more cooler and cooler...
  Finally though of our wrong decision taken on cloths.....
